query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(mc mi t it) NoMergeJoin(it mc mi t ct) */ select min(t.title) AS american_movie
from title AS t
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 1994 AND mc.note not like '%(TV)%' AND mc.note like '%(USA)%'
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Danish',
'American',
'Denish',
'Bulgaria',
'Denmark',
'America',
'Norwegian',
'Norway',
'Germany',
'USA')
inner join info_type AS it
on it.id = mi.info_type_id
inner join company_type AS ct
on ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND ct.kind = 'production companies';
